msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前就老費話唔鍾意你就賣你或者掟鳩你<br />\n球員聽聽話話<br />\n現架果班球員話唔鍾意領隊就hea 鳩你 等你場場輸 迫你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難長教</blockquote><br />\n證明90後真係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes 有少少天份 就當自己大帝咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解講到呢度第一個就諗起尼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd5c196965ea3e4bd4fdb33f31dda3eae224738","tid":461263,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前就老費話唔鍾意你就賣你或者掟鳩你<br />\n球員聽聽話話<br />\n現架果班球員話唔鍾意領隊就hea 鳩你 等你場場輸 迫你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難長教</blockquote><br />\n證明90後真係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原因係博斯克法案<br />\n<br />\n係呢個法案前 球員就算完左約 都唔可以自由轉會  果陣時球員點敢同球會，教練搞到咁僵 激怒左 一陣走都無得走<br />\n<br />\n(所謂歐盟的自由化政策 徹底摧毀左一堆二線聯賽)"},{"pid":"dce93fbc3249b65e2541eda8beed7d6496fb9047","tid":461263,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"博斯克法案 個意思係咩<br />\n<br />\n山齊士得返一年都無用<br />\n<br />\n唔同球會deal 一個大家可以接受的方案<br />\n續約+解約金 or 生效年期較後的解約條款<br />\n<br />\n出年 完約 唔撚駛踢<br />\n<br />\nhea踢 渣流灘 等好嗎出現<br />\n<br />\n同費格遜仲有90後有咩關係"},{"pid":"539a63237e8db9126048d078baf161faa1a3a5f3","tid":461263,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教得長，好多冠軍<br />\n<br />\n根本就係雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抽夠未呀死曼狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac